31
00:02:26,804 --> 00:02:29,970
Please do not give out
your names so carelessly.

32
00:02:30,004 --> 00:02:33,404
Instead, let's value our lives.

33
00:02:33,437 --> 00:02:35,304
-I knew that he needed
a face to kill someone,

34
