needed a name, too.

36
00:02:38,704 --> 00:02:40,670
-There's no way to verify
if this is related,

37
00:02:40,704 --> 00:02:43,504
but criminals whose names
were never released publicly

38
00:02:43,537 --> 00:02:45,870
or whose names were spelled
incorrectly in the media

39
00:02:45,904 --> 00:02:47,470
have not been targeted.

40
00:02:47,504 --> 00:02:50,904
We briefly went over it
at one of our meetings.

41
00:02:50,937 --> 00:02:52,470
L: That's enough
small talk for now.

42
00:02:52,504 --> 00:02:53,637
Come this way.

43
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:55,037
-Oh, uh, right.

44
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:57,537
L: Please turn off all
your cellphones, handhelds,

45
00:02:57,570 --> 00:02:59,270
and any other
communication devices

46
