to leak information?

49
00:03:06,737 --> 00:03:07,404
-It's all right.

50
00:03:07,437 --> 00:03:09,470
Just do as he says.

51
00:03:09,504 --> 00:03:11,237
TOUTA MATSUDA: I realize
he's been cautious

52
00:03:11,270 --> 00:03:12,970
from the very
beginning, but I still

53
00:03:13,004 --> 00:03:15,170
can't tell if he
trusts us or not.

54
00:03:15,204 --> 00:03:16,670
L: No, I just find
them distracting.

55
00:03:16,704 --> 00:03:19,070
I can't stand it when
people's cell phones are

56
00:03:19,104 --> 00:03:21,737
ringing while I'm
trying to talk.

57
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:24,470
Let me start by saying nobody
takes notes on anything

58
00:03:24,504 --> 00:03:25,770
that's said in these meetings.

59
00:03:25,804 --> 00:03:27,337
That means when we
leave headquarters,

60
00:03:27,370 --> 00:03:30,937
any information we need
is committed to memory.

61
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:33,537
Please, make
yourselves comfortable.

62
00:03:33,570 --> 00:03:34,804
-Uh, right.

63
